com.htsmart.wristband2.bean

Class WristbandConfig

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.htsmart.wristband2.bean.WristbandConfig
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    BytesEnabled

    public class WristbandConfig
extends java.lang.Object
implements BytesEnabled
    Contains all wristband configuration and wristband version info. WristbandVersion NotificationConfig PageConfig FunctionConfig HealthyConfig SedentaryConfig DrinkWaterConfig BloodPressureConfig TurnWristLightingConfig WarnHeartRateConfig WarnBloodPressureConfig NotDisturbConfig WomenHealthyConfig

    If WristbandVersion.isExtWarnHeartRate() is false, the warnHeartRateConfig will be null. If WristbandVersion.isExtWarnBloodPressure() is false, the warnBloodPressureConfig will be null. If WristbandVersion.isExtNotDisturb() is false, the notDisturbConfig will be null. If WristbandVersion.isWomenHealthyEnabled() is false, the womenHealthyConfig will be null. If WristbandVersion.isExtProtectionReminder() is false, the protectionReminderConfig will be null. If WristbandVersion.isExtHandWashingReminder() is false, the handWashingReminderConfig will be null.
